          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 158,
              "endIndex": 268,
              "text": "The short answer: **Standard microneedling** is excellent for general texture and mild anti-aging on a budget."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              0
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 269,
              "endIndex": 412,
              "text": "A **PRP facial** (microneedling with Platelet-Rich Plasma) is better for deep acne scars, advanced wrinkles, and those who want faster healing."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              2,
              3
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 450,
              "endIndex": 616,
              "text": "| Feature | Standard Microneedling | PRP Facial (\"Vampire Facial\") |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| **How it Works** | Tiny needles create micro-injuries to boost collagen."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              4,
