          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 1674,
              "endIndex": 1829,
              "text": "When a PRP Facial is Better\nOften called the **Vampire Facial**, this treatment uses your own blood's platelets to \"supercharge\" the microneedling process."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              12,
              7,
              5
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 2125,
              "endIndex": 2223,
              "text": "*   **Reduced Downtime:** Surprisingly, though it involves blood, the PRP acts as a healing serum."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              6,
              14
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 2362,
              "endIndex": 2495,
              "text": "*   **The Verdict:** Choose this if you have specific, stubborn skin damage or want the \"gold standard\" of non-surgical rejuvenation."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              3
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 2539,
              "endIndex": 2618,
              "text": "*   **Standard Microneedling:** Temporary redness, swelling, and minor peeling."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              4
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 2727,
              "endIndex": 2828,
              "text": "*   **PRP Facial:** Includes all the risks of microneedling, plus the added step of a **blood draw**."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              12
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 2927,
              "endIndex": 3034,
              "text": "However, because PRP uses your own blood, there is zero risk of an allergic reaction to the \"serum\" itself."
